1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:54,420 --> 00:02:00,020
Go Ahead

3
00:02:00,140 --> 00:02:02,860
Episode 35

4
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,480
But this bridge is just inconvenient for me.

5
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,080
As you can see,

6
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,080
this 3-room house with the area of 140 square meters

7
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,080
is north-facing,

8
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,720
and it’s newly-decorated for a newly married couple

9
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,800
who didn’t live here for long.

10
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,920
So this house

11
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,320
is really a great choice.

12
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,840
But it is too big

13
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:18,920
and not many people want such a big house,

14
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:19,520
but I think it's just right for you

15
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,240
to live in.

16
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,720
The house is nice,

17
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:24,600
but it's better

18
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,880
if the rent is much lower.

19
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,920
Later I'll discuss it with the landlord

20
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,880
to see if they can lower the rent

21
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,280
if you can pay it annually.

22
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,160
OK, that's great.

23
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,440
Thank you.

24
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,079
You're welcome.

25
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,200
OK, goodbye.

26
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,160
See you.

27
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,280
OK.

28
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,920
This house is excellent.

29
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,520
Indeed, it is big enough.

30
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,800
When your brother comes to live with us,

31
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,600
there's enough room for him too.

32
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,520
Well, you can live here yourself.

33
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,640
I'll return to Singapore on the weekend.

34
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:53,200
Now that your brother and I are here,

35
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,800
why do you return to Singapore yourself?

36
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,120
Then I'll go to Malaysia

37
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,650
to be with my grandparents.

38
00:02:58,200 --> 00:03:00,280
Cut it out, OK?

39
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,650
Besides, I've been used to living here

40
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,000
since I was little.

41
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,520
This is my home.

42
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,260
What's wrong with you?

43
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,320
We've agreed

44
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,480
to come back to celebrate Ling Xiao's birthday

45
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,360
and sweep the tomb of my grandmother,

46
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,120
but why did you decide

47
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,180
to settle down here

48
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:17,000
after discussing it with uncle?

49
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:18,760
I just think

50
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,920
it is well developed here,

51
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:23,120
and it’s convenient to live here.

52
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,360
Besides, you like this place,

53
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,480
don't you?

54
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,040
You were happy

55
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,100
to go fishing with your uncle, right?

56
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,280
You miss your brother a lot too, right?

57
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,400
I don't!

58
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,160
Can't you see

59
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,840
that he doesn’t want us here?

60
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,320
No.

61
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,650
You are yelling at me again.

62
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,120
I want to come back home, so what?

63
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,360
What’s wrong with it?

64
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,440
I want to stay with my family.

65
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,000
So what?

66
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:55,520
And you

67
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,720
yell at me

68
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,620
and get angry with me all the time.

69
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,480
If we return to Singapore,

70
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,200
I have to tolerate it every day.

71
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:03,280
I deserve

72
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,680
to be alone in Singapore?

73
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:27,640
In fact, I didn’t plan this.

74
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,320
After all,

75
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,920
I'm already used to the life

76
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,920
in Singapore.

77
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,920
However, what your uncle said

78
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,159
does make sense.

79
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,159
As you are in China,

80
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,680
you will have to fly to Singapore

81
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,840
if something happens to me

82
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,320
when I'm old.

83
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,600
So I'd rather return to China now.

84
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,840
Indeed that's right.

85
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,600
You can come back.

86
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,520
However, Chengzi will be in her senior year in high school

87
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,120
after this summer holiday,

88
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,680
and she will take the college entrance exam next year.

89
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,600
The education in Singapore

90
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,000
is different from that in China,

91
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,080
and she cannot transfer to a school here either.

92
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,280
There will be a great impact on her.

93
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,080
If you want to live here,

94
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,320
what’s she supposed to do?

95
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,840
So this is what you worry about?

96
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,400
I've already thought about it.

97
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,120
Since she's on summer holiday now,

98
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,320
we'll be back to Singapore

99
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,450
when school starts.

100
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,920
Once the winter holiday arrives, we'll come here again.

101
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,760
And we'll be back to Singapore before school starts again.

102
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,800
As taking a plane is so convenient now,

103
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,920
It’ll take only a short time to go to and fro.

104
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,160
After taking the college entrance exam,

105
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,040
Chengzi can

106
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,940
apply for a domestic university.

107
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,680
There are a lot of excellent universities in China.

108
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,440
By then,

109
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,400
we'll move back completely

110
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,480
after I sell the house in Singapore.

111
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,040
It’ll take only a year.

112
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,960
You can move back

113
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,560
after Chengzi takes the college entrance examination.

114
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,200
You don't have to go travel back and forth.

115
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,159
It doesn’t matter,

116
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:38,220
Chengzi won't cause you any trouble.

117
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,520
Actually,

118
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:47,120
I just want to live somewhere close to you

119
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,920
so that I can often see you

120
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,880
and take care of you.

121
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,200
We are family,

122
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,250
so we should live together.

123
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,080
Children

124
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,720
are the main concern of their parents.

125
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,600
I'll go back to Singapore on this weekend, anyway.

126
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:10,160
OK.

127
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:13,010
You can live wherever you want,

128
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,520
but you shouldn't come back

129
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,000
until Chengzi takes her college entrance exam.

130
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,000
Like you said,

131
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:17,880
children

132
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:20,010
are the main concern of their parents.

133
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,080
Don't worry,

134
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:25,000
I won't cause you any trouble.

135
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,320
You made up your mind

136
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:26,920
when I came back from Singapore

137
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,120
the last time, right?

138
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,760
Chengzi told me

139
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,320
that you bought a lot of things

140
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,050
and went to visit your friends.

141
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,250
So you were saying goodbye?

142
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,720
You asked me

143
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,760
to hang out with my friends, didn't you?

144
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,600
You told me

145
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,640
to go shopping, have some coffee

146
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,080
and go out in the sun.

147
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,240
Anyway you don't believe

148
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,500
in whatever I tell you.

149
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,920
Yeah, it's my fault.

150
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,480
It's my fault.

151
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,440
I have bad luck.

152
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,120
I didn't even meet my mom for the last time

153
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,720
before she passed away.

154
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,440
I had a car accident

155
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,920
and lost my husband,

156
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,600
and I became what I'm right now.

157
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,130
I'm a burden to my children.

158
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,760
No wonder you despise me.

159
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,320
Who despises you?

160
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:11,240
Stop pretending to be pathetic!

161
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,200
Chengzi!

162
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:12,960
This is

163
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,020
what you think too!

164
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,000
How hypocritical!

165
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,640
Shut up!

166
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,360
Can't I even tell the truth?

167
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:20,360
You don’t let me tell the truth just because you don’t?

168
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,460
What brought you back, Jianjian?

169
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,000
Since

170
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,600
Ms. Chen Ting and Chengzi

171
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,360
are going back to Singapore soon,

172
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,800
I bought some local specialties.

173
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:38,960
But they were delivered to my studio

174
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,720
by mistake,

175
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,250
so I carried them back here.

176
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,159
I'm leaving.

177
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,520
You’re sweating.

178
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,800
I'm going back to the hotel.

179
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,680
Mom!

180
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,100
Are you coming with me?

181
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,730
Then you just stay here.

182
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,980
I've made up my mind to come back to China.

183
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,570
If you don’t want

184
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,040
to see me,

185
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,160
it’s up to you.

186
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:46,800
Xiao?

187
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,580
Your mom and you sister have left?

188
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,120
I'm in a sweat. What happened?

189
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,280
What happened?

190
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,480
Do you want me to hold you like a baby?

191
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,920
My mom wants to rent a house

192
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,520
in our residential quarter.

193
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,740
She wants to settle down here.

194
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,880
I didn’t see that coming.

195
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,850
She must have made up her mind long ago.

196
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,520
So be it.

197
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,240
She can live

198
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,440
wherever she wants.

199
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,480
Besides,

200
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,760
It’s her hometown here,

201
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,880
and now you are back too.

202
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,840
But what about Chengzi?

203
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,140
She has to go to school.

204
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:59,480
Chengzi, your brother is cooking.

205
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,740
I've made a glass of orange juice for you.

206
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,160
Chengzi?

207
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,080
I'm back.

208
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,360
Welcome back.

209
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:19,600
Get a bowl of rice for Mingyue, Jianjian.

210
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,280
OK.

211
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,640
No, thanks, I have no appetite.

212
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,600
Why?

213
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,200
You don’t feel well?

214
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,040
No.

215
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,020
My mom blacklisted my mobile number,

216
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,960
and my dad didn't answer my call.

217
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,440
I know that my mom

218
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,840
didn't allow him to do so.

219
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,320
Would you like to go back home?

220
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,660
Forget it. I’ll give them some time to calm down.

221
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,820
I'm going to take a shower.

222
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,280
All of you are poor

223
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,480
and unfortunate.

224
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,240
Xiao,

225
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:06,360
call Chengzi.

226
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,480
Has she got back to the hotel?

227
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:10,610
I called her, but she didn't answer it.

228
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,000
Leave her alone.

229
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:13,840
Yes,

230
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,000
being at this age,

231
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,560
she's right in the middle of her rebellious period

232
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,200
and she’s against the whole world.

233
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,530
We have experienced it.

234
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,280
Remember?

235
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,400
I always

236
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,440
went to the internet bar to play games.

237
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,680
Snacks were forbidden in the class,

238
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:25,320
but I insisted on bring them.

239
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,280
I always did the opposite

240
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,120
of what the teachers said.

241
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:27,650
Exactly.

242
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,880
At that time,

243
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,440
I got changed immediately after school.

244
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,680
I thought that the school uniform

245
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:35,000
was too ugly.

246
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,000
Well, you were like a punk.

247
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,000
I just pretended to be.

248
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,000
The children nowadays

249
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,240
are much difficult than what we used to be.

250
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:45,000
They do short videos.

251
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,840
They just need more homework.

252
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,160
Indeed.

253
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,200
The children nowadays

254
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,320
could play with iPads at the age of two.

255
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,080
They have their own minds

256
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,360
very early.

257
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:18,720
Why are you

258
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,480
sitting here?

259
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,340
Watch out for the bad guys.

260
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,600
Go home.

261
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,640
What are you doing?

262
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,320
What are you doing?

263
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,400
Pal?

264
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,680
Pal,

265
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,240
are you OK?

266
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,160
Do you need me

267
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:41,840
to get a taxi for you?

268
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,440
No.

269
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,720
Thank you. Thank you.

270
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:46,800
Someone will pick me up.

271
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,320
You don't need my help, right?

272
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,160
Thank you.

273
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,600
Thank you.

274
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,080
OK.

275
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,440
What's the matter?

276
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,800
It's already 10 p.m.

277
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,770
The hotel is right here.

278
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,120
Why don't you go back?

279
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,920
I had a quarrel with my mom.

280
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,880
She keeps all of my certificates,

281
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,080
so I can't book a room.

282
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,720
You see,

283
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,160
if I hadn’t

284
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:09,840
passed by after work,

285
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,720
are you going to sit here all night long?

286
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,320
Does your brother know this?

287
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:25,800
Hello, Ling Xiao.

288
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,720
I’ve got your sister in my hands.

289
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,360
Gosh! She's eating my...

290
