586
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:10,460
she’ll think that she’s not good enough for you.

587
00:25:12,320 --> 00:25:13,160
She told me

588
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:15,080
she was unfamiliar with Jianjian,

589
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:16,280
so she didn’t know what to say to her.

590
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:18,010
