591
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:20,960
Dad.

592
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:23,380
You went to see her?

593
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:25,960
No. Why would I do that?

594
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,440
I just called

595
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:30,320
and asked her

596
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,440
if she needs me to help her move.

597
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,240
And I asked her

598
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,960
about Jianjian and you, by the way.

599
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:36,220
That's why she told me about it like that.

600
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,240
Dad.

601
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,320
Thank you.

602
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,160
Ling Xiao,

603
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,240
I used to...

604
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:52,920
Dad.

605
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:55,200
When I was in fourth grade,

606
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,080
I wrote an essay

607
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,220
about "My Dad".

608
00:25:57,760 --> 00:25:58,640
Do you still remember it?

609
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,160
Of course I remember it.

610
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:02,100
You wrote about Mr. Li.

611
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,600
Don't mention this to me.

612
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:04,960
I'm still annoyed.

613
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:08,010
Actually I wrote about you.

614
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:10,720
Really?

615
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:12,000
I wrote about you

616
00:26:12,000 --> 00:26:13,260
at the very beginning.

617
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:14,040
Then,

618
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,320
my teacher asked me to bring it back home

619
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:16,520
and let you sign on it,

620
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:18,180
so I wrote another one.

621
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,730
Did you complain about me in it,

622
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:25,360
so you dare not show it to me?

623
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,000
No.

624
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,960
I wrote

625
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,920
that my dad is a policeman

626
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:33,920
who gets rid of the wicked

627
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:36,200
and protects the civilians outside.

628
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,660
He's particularly great.

629
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,100
In fact, I admired you a lot

630
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:48,120
when I was little,

631
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:50,440
so I was too embarrassed

632
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,640
to show you the essay.

633
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,760
I wrote about Mr. Li,

634
00:26:53,760 --> 00:26:54,840
because it would make him happy

635
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:57,570
and then he would make more delicious food for me.

636
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:01,400
What a foodie you are!

637
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,240
All right, eat some meat.

638
00:27:04,840 --> 00:27:05,440
Ling Xiao,

639
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:07,280
