642
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:11,680
No, you must have kept it.

643
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,240
Show it to me.

644
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:40,240
One more mango juice.

645
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:46,000
