646
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,520
A mango juice.

647
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:48,360
OK.

648
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:49,120
Don’t.

649
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,600
