668
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:17,680
and it has nothing to do with me,

669
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,480
OK?

670
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:24,220
Apologize.

671
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,160
I'm sorry.

672
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:28,120
