673
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,840
Ziqiu.

674
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:34,420
Go watch your play.

675
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,520
Make a glass of mango juice for my little sister.

676
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:38,080
OK.

677
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:40,000
