678
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,440
It's not for sale.

679
00:28:52,080 --> 00:28:52,740
Do you think

680
00:28:53,840 --> 00:28:55,840
I can’t handle a little kid like you?

681
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:02,180
Hello, here's your Espresso.

682
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:04,840
Welcome.

683
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:16,880
