684
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:19,570
Am I disturbing you?

685
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,000
No.

686
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:23,080
Where is Dongdong?

687
00:29:23,080 --> 00:29:24,960
I got him into another kindergarten.

688
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:26,320
Your dad helped.

689
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:27,840
He's already there.

690
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,360
Is he

691
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,010
