697
00:29:44,120 --> 00:29:45,120
Poor boy.

698
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:47,000
Yes.

699
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:49,280
His mother too.

700
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,120
But it's OK.

701
00:29:51,640 --> 00:29:52,640
