in a few months.

703
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:55,800
Dongdong will get better.

704
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:05,640
I've watched the video.

705
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:09,520
Yesterday you took Dongdong

706
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,800
to my dad's noodle restaurant to have noodles.

707
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:13,080
Miss Zhu thought my dad

708
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:14,480
is still in love with you.

709
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:17,240
I mean,

710
00:30:17,760 --> 00:30:18,560
actually

711
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:20,000
a lot of people think

712
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,000
that my dad is still in love with you.

713
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,320
Wait a minute.

714
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,360
I packed it.

715
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:40,960
Give it to Dongdong.

716
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,160
Thank you

717
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,660
on behalf of Dongdong.

718
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:46,770
You’re welcome.

719
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,560
Then I'll go back to work.

720
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:49,600
Ziqiu.

721
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,760
