740
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,760
It's not Miss Zhang?

741
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:37,600
No.

742
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,040
Then,

743
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:40,200
Ms. He Mei?

