00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:43,400
Then it’s Ms. He Mei.

746
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:45,120
Seriously, no.

747
00:32:45,560 --> 00:32:46,480
Alright!

748
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,200
I believe you.

749
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:52,480
Anyway, you're at this age already.

750
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:54,320
I shouldn't talk too much about it.

