00:34:29,560 --> 00:34:30,150
You know?

811
00:34:30,190 --> 00:34:30,760
You...

812
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:33,920
Prepare your dishes.

813
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:40,400
He is so wordy.

814
00:34:43,710 --> 00:34:45,040
What "friend"?

815
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:46,360
You want to know her?

816
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:49,100
Keeping secrets for your dad!

817
00:34:50,190 --> 00:34:51,800
Why did you send my dad away?

818
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:55,880
Well...

819
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:59,040
