I know you saw that.

828
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:16,680
You're upset, right?

829
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:18,800
I'm fine.

830
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:19,920
We don't have to

831
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,840
face each other every day anyway.

832
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,600
It's alright.

833
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,680
Alright?

