840
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:34,760
Jianjian,

841
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,560
as you know, the most difficult thing in the world

842
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,690
is the relationship

843
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:38,960
