846
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,640
I will protect you

847
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:44,010
and give her a hard time.

848
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:52,260
I'm going to talk to your dad about his "friend."

849
00:35:52,600 --> 00:35:53,520
His "friend"!

850
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:16,920
Ling Xiao?

851
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,920
You came to pick me up?

852
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,640
Dad said you were

853
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:22,640
