862
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:42,800
If Ziqiu were here,

863
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,040
he would buy me one.

864
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:46,760
But he's not here.

865
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,800
Let's go.

866
00:36:59,680 --> 00:37:00,640
Did you

867
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:01,970
