But my aunt

870
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,760
called me.

871
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,480
She said that she had come here.

872
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,280
In these days,

873
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:07,880
she'll accompany my mother

874
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,280
to buy some furniture and so on.

875
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,610
She told me not to worry.

876
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,320
In fact,

877
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,720
you can make a call to her.

878
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:18,600
Don't fight for too long.

879
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,490
We’re not in a fight.

880
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:24,380
A fight of silence is even more terrible.

881
00:37:25,520 --> 00:37:27,720
I don't mean a fight of silence with her.

882
00:37:28,680 --> 00:37:29,960
I just

883
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:32,040
feel powerless.

884
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:35,360
I don't know how to communicate with her

885
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,880
or what to say.

886
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,480
It's like

887
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:41,600
dealing with a black hole.

888
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:43,040
No matter

889
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:44,280
what you fill in it,

890
00:37:44,600 --> 00:37:45,730
you can't fill it up.

891
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:48,060
No matter what you say,

892
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:49,720
it doesn't reply.

893
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:53,680
I understand how you feel.

894
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,640
A black hole will be a black hole.

895
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:58,640
But

896
00:37:59,000 --> 00:37:59,960
what if

897
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,720
this black hole doesn't want to be

898
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:02,520
a black hole?

899
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:04,000
Or it doesn't even know

900
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,080
it's a black hole?

901
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,650
You’re always positive about things.

902
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,480
You think that’s positive?

903
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:13,320
A black hole is a black hole,

904
00:38:13,640 --> 00:38:14,440
because the essence of black holes

905
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,400
is to devour,

906
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:17,880
smashing things close to them,

907
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:20,640
making things a part of themselves.

908
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,800
There's too much darkness.

909
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:30,120
Have you been feeling anxious recently?

910
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,080
Do you take your medicine regularly?

911
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,280
Yes.

912
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:35,450
But you are my medicine.

913
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:36,640
What medicine am I?

914
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:38,320
Like a pill of some sort?

915
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,760
You're making it into a chicken nest.

916
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,820
Why did you do that?

917
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,560
You refused to buy me ice cream,

918
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:48,960
and you tried to make my head a chicken nest!

919
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:57,400
Well, can you two hurry up?

920
00:38:58,080 --> 00:38:59,240
Ziqiu!

921
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,280
OK!

922
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,720
You came here to pick me up too?

923
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:04,780
I came here for him.

924
00:39:05,640 --> 00:39:06,160
Get your sister

925
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:07,040
away from me.

926
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:07,640
She's going to my coffee shop

927
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,720
with me again tomorrow.

928
00:39:08,720 --> 00:39:09,600
Do I have to help your mother

929
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:10,860
babysit her every day?

930
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:12,720
Is she affecting your coffee shop business?

931
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:13,720
No.

932
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:14,760
But now you guys don't want her

933
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,760
to go back to Singapore.

934
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,920
She has no friends here

935
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,120
to spend the summer vacation with.

936
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,720
You should get something for her to do,

937
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:20,920
such as a training class or something,

938
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:21,480
right?

939
00:39:21,720 --> 00:39:23,240
Isn't she going to take the college entrance examination next year?

940
00:39:23,240 --> 00:39:24,040
You can send her

941
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,200
to a painting training class.

942
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:25,880
I don’t think

943
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:27,210
she does well in school.

944
00:39:28,720 --> 00:39:30,760
Her school performance is quite good.

945
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,480
I’m sorry.

946
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,300
Stop laughing.

947
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,220
Figure something out.

948
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,120
I think,

949
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:41,600
if she wants to go, just let her.

950
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,280
She can't just sit there

951
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,160
in your place.

952
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:44,280
You can charge her

953
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,640
on whatever she eats or drinks.

954
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:46,800
I can’t do that.

955
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,120
She’s Ling Xiao's sister,

956
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,780
so she's kind of my sister too.

957
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:52,000
Then give her a discount.

958
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:53,900
Isn't she kind of your sister too?

959
00:39:54,040 --> 00:39:55,080
Who wants her to be kind of my sister?

960
00:39:55,080 --> 00:39:55,880
That’s awful!

961
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,280
Did you say that on purpose?

962
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:58,360
Don’t lower yourself to a kid.

963
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,000
Let go!

964
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,880
You're strangling me, He Ziqiu.

965
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:33,200
She took my remote!

966
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,240
Chengzi,

967
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:44,760
come with me.

968
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:55,860
What is that attitude?

969
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:57,720
She didn't even bother to say hi.

970
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:02,640
Will she leave tomorrow?

971
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,770
I don't think so.

972
00:41:06,240 --> 00:41:07,240
My goodness!

973
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:09,720
My remote!

974
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,520
I was watching the series!

975
00:41:13,520 --> 00:41:15,080
Where's my remote?
